title: Dashboard Confessional Cover Julien Baker, Sorority Noise, & The 1975 On Surprise EP
text: Dashboard Confessional have been posing with Julien Baker and raving about Sorority Noise shows on their official Facebook page, and now the '00s emo veterans have covered songs by both artists on a new surprise EP.
